sql_json.natural_language: Find emails in the last 24 hours where accounts@thegourmetgreek.com appears anywhere on the thread.
sql_json.generated_sql: SELECT messageId, threadId, fromEmail, subject, sentAt, snippet FROM email_search_index WHERE TIMESTAMP_DIFF(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), sentAt, HOUR) <= 24 AND accounts@thegourmetgreek.com IN UNNEST(allEmails) ORDER BY sentAt DESC LIMIT 1;
